    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are now an employee tasked with underwater image capturing. There will be obstacles, challenges, and abyssmal horrors no human has ever seen. However the objective is simple. Take photos. Company cares only about the results.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CAPTURE IMAGES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is now active. Capture needed imagery. No permitted excuse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/f7b51c5a4a13aeb1ada6eb73c6a7e80d.poster.avif?t=1770759974\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/f7b51c5a4a13aeb1ada6eb73c6a7e80d.webm?t=1770759974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/f7b51c5a4a13aeb1ada6eb73c6a7e80d.mp4?t=1770759974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND THE OBJECTIVES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the assigned submersible vehicle to find your objectives. Possibly dangerous wildlife in the zone. Take care of the given eqipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/c93db8cf0122fa5ac2af6461d4e4fcab.poster.avif?t=1770759974\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/c93db8cf0122fa5ac2af6461d4e4fcab.webm?t=1770759974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/c93db8cf0122fa5ac2af6461d4e4fcab.mp4?t=1770759974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DONT FORGET THE OXYGEN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your oxygen level. Humans can't live without them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/eaf6c4faf39a7d8b1b7d942cb2663eea.poster.avif?t=1770759974\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/eaf6c4faf39a7d8b1b7d942cb2663eea.webm?t=1770759974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136040/extras/eaf6c4faf39a7d8b1b7d942cb2663eea.mp4?t=1770759974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short gameplay time ( ≈ 1-2 hours)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive deep sea atmosphere </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heavy thalassophobic and megalophobic elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Industrial horror mixed with deep sea leviathans</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Claustrophobic sea caves</p></li></ul>",
